room_title: Escape room "Aunt Edna's Condo" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: We did Aunt Edna's condo with Chels. She was fantastic. Explained everything very well and was so friendly. The room was challenging, and the clues were very creative.  There were neat features that I didn't expect. I would definitely recommend this escape room!

room_title: Escape room "Aunt Edna's Condo" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: We had an absolute blast sleuthing our way through Edna's condo - with some help from Ella! Such a fun night!

room_title: Escape room "Aunt Edna's Condo" by Expedition Escape in King of Prussia
review: A small group of us did Aunt Edna's Condo and successfully escaped! Morgan was our guide and she was excellent. She helped us with clues when we needed it and explained each puzzle to us in the end. Overall a great experience. I would do it again!
